Subject HIV - infected persons and Thalidomide Victims Association Order - Exemption from residency requirement - 3(a)(ii)
PrecisOrder which exempts an individual from the residency requirements of the HIV-INFECTED PERSONS AND THALIDOMIDE VICTIMS ASSISTANCE ORDER, enacted by Order in Council P.C. 1990-4/872 of May 10, 1990, and thus renders him eligible to receive the benefits provided for therein.
